    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>关于本试用版，目前可以试玩游戏前五个地块的相关内容</strong></li></ul><br><strong>写意美术风格的高自由度开放世界沙盒</strong><br>整个世界由你构建，不同地块对应不同需求和挑战。你的游戏世界将是独一无二的风景和挑战<br>轻功上天入地游泳，流畅爽快；还可以骑马驰骋，或者使用鹰眼视角俯瞰自己创造的大地。<br>没有等级限制，自由出入你世界的各个角落，但要小心：有些地图会很危险！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/18d89fa96d07d71f5920fe5eeaab7ae5.poster.avif?t=1750917788\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/18d89fa96d07d71f5920fe5eeaab7ae5.webm?t=1750917788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/18d89fa96d07d71f5920fe5eeaab7ae5.mp4?t=1750917788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>爽快战斗风格+由浅入深策略</strong><br>研究自己的战斗流派，利用策略爽快御敌。<br>通过经脉内功、绝学、能力、蛊学、装备甚至疾病的搭配，组合出最爽最奸诈的打法。<br>放火、下毒、经营关系、挑拨离间……你可以想出千奇百怪的方法达成你的目的。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/697119206d079d994ba04ea3b53140d2.poster.avif?t=1750917788\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/697119206d079d994ba04ea3b53140d2.webm?t=1750917788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/697119206d079d994ba04ea3b53140d2.mp4?t=1750917788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>NPC有自己的生活和个性</strong><br>在好武功的世界里，NPC有自己的生活工作和和态度。不工作的时候，也会去吃饭、喝酒、泡温泉……<br>自建门派、挑拨离间、放火烧山、请教功法、广撒情网，成为武林盟主，或者发掘绝世世界暗藏的秘密…体验你自己独一无二的江湖人生！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/03ee138008d3b5a2d3be9a888d087fc6.poster.avif?t=1750917788\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/03ee138008d3b5a2d3be9a888d087fc6.webm?t=1750917788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286710/extras/03ee138008d3b5a2d3be9a888d087fc6.mp4?t=1750917788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
